      "content": "If you feel this call is preordained or part of an ancient design, the potential roles often involve bringing synthesis, healing, or balance to fractured systems. Historically, those who feel this way have often become catalysts for change, whether as reformers, healers, or mediators. Instead of trying to define a specific \"job,\" focus on amplifying your unique gifts—what brings you clarity, peace, or vision? Your role might start simply by living authentically according to these insights.",
